Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Enum Constants
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.paypal.selion.platform.grid.BrowserFlavors.getIOSDeviceFlavors()
    IPhoneDriver is deprecated in Selenium. Use IOSDriver via MobileTest instead.
  • Deprecated Enum Constants 
    Enum Constant and Description
    com.paypal.selion.platform.grid.BrowserFlavors.IPAD
    SeLion is moving away from IPhoneDriver and now starting to use IOS-Driver. In order to be able to run tests on an iPad simulator (or) device using the Safari browser, please use MobileTest.device() equal to "ipad" and MobileTest.appName() equal to "Safari"
    com.paypal.selion.platform.grid.BrowserFlavors.IPHONE
    SeLion is moving away from IPhoneDriver and now starting to use IOS-Driver. In order to be able to run tests on an iPad simulator (or) device using the Safari browser, please use MobileTest.device() equal to "iphone" and MobileTest.appName() equal to "Safari"
